snippet.title: Don't Spill Your Coffee! Now On Steam Greenlight!
snippet.description:
The YouTube hit game Don't Spill Your Coffee! is now up for voting on Steam Greenlight! We need your support to get our game on Steam.

Please vote here: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=688736382

...and let the community know that you would like to see Don't Spill Your Coffee available in the Steam library. This will go a long way in getting the Supremo Edition available for a wide release!

Want to give the Game Jam version of Don't Spill Your Coffee that so many YouTubers have enjoyed a shot?

Try it out here: https://symphonite.itch.io/dont-spill-your-coffee

Thanks everyone!
